            <bug_when>2011-01-15 13:39:44 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>Consider this generator error message:

&gt;&gt;&gt; Switched variants:
  - qx.debug = o
&gt;&gt;&gt; Resolving dependencies
  -  **.*.*..*.Error: Variantoptimizer: No default case found for (qx.debug:off)
 at (qx.core.Property:1004)

when the config wrongly sets a string instead of an array as variant value (here, for qx.debug).

The error message should hint at the current variant value, which cannot be matched to the alternatives in the current select statment.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
          <long_desc isprivate="0">
