            <bug_when>2011-01-15 14:01:59 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>Improved error logging, and added a check that all variant map values must be list. This map checking is a premature workaround, in the absence of a more general schema checking of config files, hopefully to come.

With r24560.</thetext>
